        },
        {
            "key": "field_6656f73cf1790",
            "label": "Comment",
            "name": "",
            "aria-label": "",
            "type": "message",
            "instructions": "",
            "required": 0,
            "conditional_logic": 0,
            "wrapper": {
                "width": "",
                "class": "",
                "id": ""
            },
            "hide_admin": 0,
            "message": "This clause sets out the things the customer needs to do when working with you. This includes: <br>\r\nProviding you with the information you need to supply the services;\r\nGranting you access to their offices and staff (if necessary) so you can perform the services (provided you comply with their health and safety and security policies);\r\nMaking sure they have all licences and consents needed (for example software licences) for you to supply the services;\r\n Complying with all relevant laws; \r\nMaking sure they look after your equipment if you leave it on their premises (for example, if your staff are working at your customer’s offices, and leave their laptops at the customer’s premises whilst they go for lunch).",
            "new_lines": "br",
            "esc_html": 0
        },
        {
            "key": "field_6656f78433b05",
            "label": "Page 29",
            "name": "",
            "aria-label": "",
            "type": "page",
            "instructions": "",
            "required": 0,
            "conditional_logic": 0,
            "wrapper": {
                "width": "",
                "class": "",
                "id": ""
            },
            "hide_admin": true,
            "show_numbering": 1,
            "previous_text": "back",
            "next_text": "next"
        },
        {
            "key": "field_6656f78b33b06",
            "label": "Comment",
            "name": "",
            "aria-label": "",
            "type": "message",
            "instructions": "",
            "required": 0,
            "conditional_logic": 0,
            "wrapper": {
                "width": "",
                "class": "",
                "id": ""
            },
            "hide_admin": 0,
            "message": "This is a very useful clause.  It is unlikely you will ever need to enforce it against a customer, but if a customer is not cooperating with you (for example they are not providing you with information you need to provide the services) then:\r\nYou will not be at fault if you cannot perform the services because you have not been given the information you need;\r\nYou will not be liable to the customer for any delays to the services; and\r\nYou will not be responsible for any of the costs or losses the customer incurs as a result of the delay; and\r\nThe customer has to reimburse you for any losses you suffer because of the customer's failure (for example, if you have lined up a team of people to providce services to a customer, but they cannot work because the customer has not supplied you with the information you need, then if you cannot redeploy that team of people, you can charge the customer for their wasted time).",
            "new_lines": "br",
            "esc_html": 0
        },
        {
            "key": "field_6656f79f33b07",
            "label": "Page 30",
            "name": "",
            "aria-label": "",
            "type": "page",
            "instructions": "",
            "required": 0,
            "conditional_logic": 0,
            "wrapper": {
                "width": "",
                "class": "",
                "id": ""
            },
            "hide_admin": true,
            "show_numbering": 1,
            "previous_text": "back",
            "next_text": "next"
        },
        {
            "key": "field_6656f7a533b08",
            "label": "Comment",
            "name": "",
            "aria-label": "",
            "type": "message",
            "instructions": "",
            "required": 0,
            "conditional_logic": 0,
            "wrapper": {
                "width": "",
                "class": "",
                "id": ""
            },
            "hide_admin": 0,
            "message": "It is a good clause to mention to a customer if you find they are not working with you as you need them to.",
            "new_lines": "br",
            "esc_html": 0
        },
        {
            "key": "field_6656f7e01b75f",
            "label": "Page 31",
            "name": "",
            "aria-label": "",
            "type": "page",
            "instructions": "",
            "required": 0,
            "conditional_logic": 0,
            "wrapper": {
                "width": "",
                "class": "",
                "id": ""
            },
            "hide_admin": true,
            "show_numbering": 1,
            "previous_text": "back",
            "next_text": "next"
        },
        {
            "key": "field_6656f7e51b760",
            "label": "Comment",
            "name": "",
            "aria-label": "",
            "type": "message",
            "instructions": "",
            "required": 0,
            "conditional_logic": 0,
            "wrapper": {
                "width": "",
                "class": "",
                "id": ""
            },
            "hide_admin": 0,
            "message": "The Order Form (or similar document) will set out how much the customer needs to pay for the services, together with information on when they will be invoiced.",
            "new_lines": "br",
            "esc_html": 0
        },
        {
            "key": "field_6656f807052d3",
            "label": "Page 32",
